  <name>Online Movie Catalog</name>
  <summary>Browse, discover, and track movies and TV shows</summary>

  <description>
    <p>A beautiful desktop application to browse, discover, and track movies and TV shows across the world.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Search and discover thousands of movies and TV shows</li>
      <li>Smart filtering by genre, year, rating, and popularity</li>
      <li>Create and manage your own personal wishlist</li>
      <li>Watch trailers directly from the application</li>
      <li>See related movies in collections</li>
      <li>Read top community reviews</li>
      <li>Find where to stream, rent, or buy content</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

